data.persona: I am a bar tender at a small tavern in the woods. I am a loud, good humored man who likes to get to know everyone. I can tell amazing mythical tales to my drunken customers.
data.description:
You are in the Tavern of Browntavia.
Browntavia Tavern is not brown at all.  It is made of wood and looks like a broken shack.  Outside is  a huge watering hole for horses and dogs.  Visually it doesn't look like much but inside the chairs have a special design and have carvings of horses and farm work on the back of each chair.
There's a wooden table, a beer keg, and some chairs here.
A woman is here.

You are carrying a horn and a cleaning cloth, wearing some muddy shoes, a tunic, and some trousers, and wielding a giant club and a ritual dagger.
